<item>
            <title>[LU-327] port bug18896 to master(replay-single test_61d: @@@@@@ FAIL: cannot restart mds on Cray xt3)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-327</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;for mgc, it doesn&apos;t cleanup its obd_import if it setup the import but never connect, should add cleanup code in mgc_precleanup just like mdc_precleanup&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    /* client import will not have been cleaned. */&lt;br/&gt;
    cfs_down_write(&amp;amp;obd-&amp;gt;u.cli.cl_sem);&lt;br/&gt;
    if (obd-&amp;gt;u.cli.cl_import) &lt;/p&gt;
{
           struct obd_import *imp;
            imp = obd-&amp;gt;u.cli.cl_import;
            CERROR(&quot;client import never connected\n&quot;);
            class_destroy_import(imp);
            obd-&amp;gt;u.cli.cl_import = NULL;
    }
&lt;p&gt;    cfs_up_write(&amp;amp;obd-&amp;gt;u.cli.cl_sem);&lt;/p&gt;</description>
